                <p>
                    <lb n="1"/> <gap reason="lost" quantity="4" unit="character"/> mpi Amutaṉ tiruviḷaṅkoyil perumāṉaṭikaḷukku tiruvuṇṇāḻikai<unclear>ppuṟa</unclear>māka nūṟṟukkaḻañcu poṉ tiruccokuṉūr <hi rend="grantha">sabh</hi>aiyā <gap reason="lost" quantity="5" unit="character"/> 
                    <lb n="2"/> <gap reason="lost" quantity="3" unit="character"/> koyil perumāṉaṭikaḷukku tiruvuṇṇāḻikaippuṟam tiruvamirtu ceṟuvāka Ūriṉ kiḻai tiruvamirtu ceṟukkoṇṭu kuṭuttār tiru <gap reason="lost" quantity="5" unit="character"/> 
                    <lb n="3"/><gap reason="lost" quantity="4" unit="character"/> <hi rend="grantha"> brāhma</hi>ṇar Uṇpatāka vaitta cempoṉ pattu
                    <lb n="4"/><gap reason="lost" quantity="3" unit="character"/> <unclear>ko<!--kāl clear--></unclear>yil perumāṉaṭikaḷukku tiruvuṇṇāḻikai puṟamāka kuṭutta viḷāttoṭṭai ceṟu mu<unclear>m</unclear>māvarai <gap reason="lost" quantity="1" unit="character"/> 
                </p>
                
